<h2 id="email">Email Marketing: AWeber</h2>

Salon chains that build email lists have a significant advantage in rebooking and seasonal promotions. AWeber's reliability and simplicity make it the right fit for salon operators who don't want to manage complex email infrastructure.

<p><strong>Salon-specific email use cases:</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>Weekly or monthly newsletters with new services, seasonal specials, and stylist spotlights</li>
  <li>Automated welcome sequences for new clients captured through WiFi portal or booking system</li>
  <li>Birthday and anniversary emails with special offers</li>
  <li>Product launch announcements for retail lines carried in-salon</li>
</ul>

AWeber's deliverability is consistently excellent, which matters when your emails are competing with every other brand in your client's inbox. The automation builder handles all of the above without requiring a marketing team.

<p><strong>Cost:</strong> Free to 500 subscribers, $20/mo for paid plans.</p>

